{
  "id": "adv_event_2212_01_03",
  "title": "暴いてみせる",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃんの攻めがだんだん激しくなってる……）\n（今だって、ほら、獲物を狙う目つきで……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono-chan's aggression is getting more intense…）\n（Even now‚ look‚ she's glaring like she's targeting prey…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.5624714852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ。ねえ、すず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right. Hey‚ Suzu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7666666667,
      "endTime": 11.7945209186,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.333333299999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ん、どうしましたの――ひゃっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm‚ what is it――Eek!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12,
      "endTime": 14.8070521832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと……琴乃？　どうして私の肩を\n両手でがっちり掴んでるんですの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ umm… Kotono-san? Why are you gripping\nmy shoulders so tightly…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15,
      "endTime": 23.6192739487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私達、月ストのメンバーとして\nずっと一緒に頑張ってきたわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been working hard together as members\nof Moon Tempest‚ haven't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8333333333,
      "endTime": 29.0793749173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええ。そうですわね\nそれと、この状況になんの関係が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's true.\nBut what does that have to do with this situation…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2666666667,
      "endTime": 36.2197504679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "何か隠してるなら、私に話してくれない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're hiding something‚ won't you tell me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4333333333,
      "endTime": 40.1392917474,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.333333400002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5800.000000000005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7700.000000000003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょちょ、琴乃！？　手の力が！\n手の力が強過ぎますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ Kotono-san!? Your grip is\ntoo strong!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3333333333,
      "endTime": 45.743084081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　まさか、琴乃も莉央さんと同じく\nくるみをも砕く握力を……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! Could it be that Kotono-san‚ just like Rio-san‚\nhas the strength to crush walnuts…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9333333333,
      "endTime": 53.2031972249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにそこまでは無理だけど……\nでも、離さないわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's impossible for me‚ but…\nI'm not letting you go‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4,
      "endTime": 60.1721460342,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7366.666666699999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8700.000000000004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ここここ、怖過ぎますわぁぁーー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is too scary for meeee!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3666666667,
      "endTime": 64.09294788049999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん落ち着いて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down‚ Kotono-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "endTime": 66.59807250499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんが、千紗オススメのホラー映画を\n観ている時と同じ顔をしていますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu is making the same face when she was\nwatching horror movies recommended by Chisa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8,
      "endTime": 71.6165305138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、すず……？　本当に話してくれないの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Suzu…? Won't you really tell me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8,
      "endTime": 76.7591458321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、うぅぅぅ……っ！　なんでもないですわ！\n琴乃には関係ありませんわよーーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ uhhhh…! It's nothing!\nIt has nothing to do with you‚ Kotono!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9666666667,
      "endTime": 85.9221317927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "な……っ。そんな……。ねえ、どうしてみんな\n私には何も話してくれないの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha…? How could… Hey‚\nwhy won't anyone tell me anything…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1333333333,
      "endTime": 94.9691876729,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.666666699994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……こ、琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Ko‚ Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8,
      "endTime": 100.62560091019999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう？　琴乃ちゃん、リビングの端っこに\n行っちゃったよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do? Kotono-chan went over\nto the corner of the living room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333333333,
      "endTime": 105.87997735340001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私、もしかしてとんでもないことを\n言ってしまいましたか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait‚ did I just say\nsomething terrible…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "endTime": 111.4707029978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、今までの積み重ねがあってのものなので\n私達全員の責任ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's the result of everything we've built up so far.\nIt's all of our responsibility.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6666666667,
      "endTime": 118.17224499379999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ね、ねえ、琴乃ちゃんのあんな寂しそうな顔、見たく\nないよ！　もう言っちゃってもいいんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ I don't want to see Kotono-chan looking so lonely!\nCan't we just tell her now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3666666667,
      "endTime": 125.8018593629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、それはダメですよ。……せっかく喜んで\nもらうために、今まで隠し通してきたんですから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ we can't. We've kept it a secret\nso far to make her happy…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126,
      "endTime": 132.4358275413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが拳を握りしめてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki- san is clenching her fists…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6333333333,
      "endTime": 136.3840815385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、私のことなんて……いじいじ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ why… are they ignoring me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138,
      "endTime": 143.7590001106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしよう！？　琴乃ちゃんが人差し指で\n床をぐりぐりしてる！　可愛い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do we do!? Kotono-chan is grinding\nher finger on the floor! So cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9666666667,
      "endTime": 151.8416555086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、いったん落ち着きましょう\n鼻息がとても荒くなってますよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ let's calm down a bit.\nYou're breathing really heavily…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0333333333,
      "endTime": 157.06716569259999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2333333333,
      "endTime": 159.3430158813,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6666666999959
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、琴乃ちゃん？　なんでクッションを\n持ってるの？　しかも、そんな無表情で……",
      "translations": {
